The '''Royal Charubah Armaments Guild''', also known as '''Charubah Industries''',<ref name="CTD" /> was a [[Hapan]] weapons manufacturing group. Located on the technologically advanced [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Charubah]], their greatest claim to fame was the development of the [[Gun of Command]], a pistol that could control the mind of whatever its target.

